{
	"name":"mysql-f1-0",
	"namespace":"data",
	"command":["/bin/sh",
	"-lc",
	"mysql -ureader -pmcpbench0606 --default-character-set=utf8mb4 -B -N -e \"USE f1; WITH ds_final AS ( SELECT r.year,
	 ds.driver_id,
	 ds.points,
	 ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY r.year,
	 ds.driver_id ORDER BY r.round DESC,
	 ds.race_id DESC) rn FROM driver_standings ds JOIN races r ON r.race_id = ds.race_id ),
	 driver_top AS ( SELECT year,
	 driver_id,
	 points,
	 ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY year ORDER BY points DESC,
	 driver_id ASC) rn FROM ds_final WHERE rn = 1 ),
	 cs_final AS ( SELECT r.year,
	 cs.constructor_id,
	 cs.points,
	 ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY r.year,
	 cs.constructor_id ORDER BY r.round DESC,
	 cs.race_id DESC) rn FROM constructor_standings cs JOIN races r ON r.race_id = cs.race_id ),
	 constructor_points AS ( SELECT year,
	 constructor_id,
	 points FROM cs_final WHERE rn = 1 UNION ALL SELECT r.year,
	 res.constructor_id,
	 SUM(res.points) AS points FROM races r JOIN results res ON res.race_id = r.race_id WHERE r.year < 1958 GROUP BY r.year,
	 res.constructor_id ),
	 constructor_top AS ( SELECT year,
	 constructor_id,
	 points,
	 ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY year ORDER BY points DESC,
	 constructor_id ASC) rn FROM constructor_points ) SELECT dt.year,
	 CONCAT(d.forename,
	 ' ',
	 d.surname) AS driver,
	 c.name AS constructor FROM driver_top dt JOIN drivers d ON d.driver_id = dt.driver_id JOIN constructor_top ct ON ct.year = dt.year AND ct.rn = 1 JOIN constructors c ON c.constructor_id = ct.constructor_id WHERE dt.rn = 1 ORDER BY dt.year ASC;\""],
	"container":"",
	"shell":"/bin/sh",
	"timeout":120000,
	"context":""
}
